  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that BEIJING WEINA STAR TECHNOLOGY CO. LTD, also known as MINOSPACE, is and has been involved in \ndestabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, by providing and making available goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n",
